i386.c (output_387_binary_op): Add some braces to avoid warnings.

        * i386.c (output_387_binary_op): Add some braces to avoid warnings.
        * i386.h (REG_CLASS_CONTENTS): Similarly.

 #define REG_CLASS_CONTENTS \
-{      0,							\

      0xf,			/* Q_REGS */			\

  0x100ff,			/* GENERAL_REGS */		\

   0xff00,			/* FLOAT_REGS */		\
- 0x1ffff }
+ 0x1ffff }}
